<i>to tear up the map</i>

10
00:00:43,563 --> 00:00:50,628
<i>Now open your eyes and</i>
<i>take a look at the truth (Yeah!)</i>

11
00:00:50,937 --> 00:00:57,069
<i>There's nothing to lose,</i>
<i>so let's GO!!!</i>

12
00:00:57,210 --> 00:01:01,476
<i>We are Fighting Dreamers aiming high</i>

13
00:01:01,548 --> 00:01:05,143
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>don't care what people think about them</i>

14
00:01:05,218 --> 00:01:08,551
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>follow what they believe</i>

15
00:01:08,621 --> 00:01:12,250
<i>Oli Oli Oli Oh!</i>
<i>Just go my way</i>

16
00:01:12,325 --> 00:01:15,920
<i>Right here right now (Bang)</i>
<i>Hit it straight like a line drive!</i>

17
00:01:15,995 --> 00:01:19,487
<i>Right here right now (Burn)</i>
<i>We're gonna do it and do our best!</i>

18
00:01:19,566 --> 00:01:23,161
<i>Right here right now (Bang)</i>
<i>Hit it straight like a line drive!</i>

19
00:01:23,236 --> 00:01:27,332
<i>Right here right now (Burn)</i>
<i>We're gonna do it and do our best! BANG!</i>

20
00:01:38,195 --> 00:01:39,685
<i>Sasuke...?</i>

21
00:01:41,966 --> 00:01:43,490
<i>No... Who is he?</i>

22
00:01:43,868 --> 00:01:45,893
<i>He's got the same Sharingan</i>
<i>as Sasuke.</i>

23
00:01:47,705 --> 00:01:49,070
Really...

24
00:01:49,139 --> 00:01:51,607
who'd believe a kid like you to
have the Nine Tailed Fox in him.

25
00:01:54,178 --> 00:01:58,114
<i>Why does that guy know</i>
<i>about the Nine Tailed Fox?!</i>

26
00:01:59,650 --> 00:02:02,585
Naruto, you will come with us.

27
00:02:04,521 --> 00:02:10,255
<i>Roar, Chidori!</i>
<i>Howl, Sasuke!</i>

28
00:02:13,864 --> 00:02:15,661
<i>That guy is...close by!</i>

29
00:02:18,636 --> 00:02:19,694
<i>That guy!</i>

30
00:02:37,755 --> 00:02:38,687
Elder Brother...

31
00:02:40,090 --> 00:02:41,682
Today...

32
00:02:41,759 --> 00:02:44,922
when school's over,
help me train for a Shuriken Jutsu...

33
00:02:45,863 --> 00:02:50,197
I'm busy... Have father teach you.

34
00:02:51,535 --> 00:02:55,733
But you're better at Shuriken Jutsu,
Elder Brother...

35
00:02:56,573 --> 00:02:57,835
Even I can see that.

36
00:02:59,109 --> 00:03:02,567
You always treat me
like a pest, Elder Brother.

37
00:03:14,091 --> 00:03:15,080
Ouch!

38
00:03:17,294 --> 00:03:20,855
Forgive me Sasuke...
Some other time, okay?

39
00:03:36,113 --> 00:03:38,274
I don't have time to
pay attention to you today.

40
00:03:41,318 --> 00:03:45,414
You're always jabbing my forehead
and saying "Forgive me, Sasuke."

41
00:03:45,956 --> 00:03:49,824
You also say "not today,"
but there's never a day.

42
00:04:00,337 --> 00:04:01,395
Father.

43
00:04:01,472 --> 00:04:02,166
Huh?

44
00:04:02,239 --> 00:04:06,073
Why doesn't Elder Brother
pay any attention to me?

45
00:04:09,446 --> 00:04:12,472
That guy's a little strange...

46
00:04:13,484 --> 00:04:17,318
He's the type that doesn't really like
to become intimate with people.

47
00:04:18,222 --> 00:04:19,018
Why?

48
00:04:21,158 --> 00:04:22,125
I don't know.

49
00:04:23,527 --> 00:04:28,396
I am his father and
still I can't read that boy...

50
00:04:29,733 --> 00:04:30,495
Here!

51
00:04:30,567 --> 00:04:32,125
Your boxed lunch, Sasuke!

52
00:04:32,536 --> 00:04:34,026
If you're worried about doing
Shuriken Jutsu practice,

53
00:04:34,104 --> 00:04:36,470
I will watch you when you get home.

54
00:04:38,208 --> 00:04:40,870
They're not practices,
they're training

55
00:04:42,613 --> 00:04:44,080
See you later!

56
00:04:49,186 --> 00:04:51,654
Sasuke, are you on
your way to school?

57
00:04:51,889 --> 00:04:53,015
Yes.

58
00:04:53,390 --> 00:04:56,848
I saw Itachi earlier on.
He's really become a man.

59
00:04:57,127 --> 00:04:59,288
He's already a top-notch Shinobi.

60
00:04:59,863 --> 00:05:02,798
He graduated at the head of his class
at the Academy at the age of seven,

61
00:05:02,866 --> 00:05:05,198
and attained Chunin level
at the age of ten, didn't he?

62
00:05:06,537 --> 00:05:09,370
He became adept at using
Sharingan at the age of eight.

63
00:05:11,475 --> 00:05:13,466
Yes, I remember.

64
00:05:13,544 --> 00:05:17,776
That boy is truly
the pride of the Uchiha clan.

65
00:05:18,515 --> 00:05:21,348
By the way,
how old are you now, Sasuke?

66
00:05:23,987 --> 00:05:27,980
<i>I'm the same age as</i>
<i>when Elder Brother graduated,</i>

67
00:05:28,058 --> 00:05:29,047
<i>but I can't...</i>

68
00:05:29,927 --> 00:05:31,224
What's the matter?

69
00:05:31,295 --> 00:05:32,125
Hey!

70
00:05:32,930 --> 00:05:35,091
Stop talking nonsense!

71
00:05:35,466 --> 00:05:36,592
Oh my, dear.

72
00:05:37,935 --> 00:05:41,336
Sasuke, both you and Itachi
come from the same Uchiha clan,

73
00:05:41,405 --> 00:05:43,600
the pedigree of
the Hidden Leaf Village

74
00:05:44,074 --> 00:05:45,302
Have confidence!

75
00:05:45,976 --> 00:05:49,503
You'll be an amazing
Shinobi just like Itachi one day.

76
00:05:50,747 --> 00:05:51,577
Yeah!

77
00:05:52,382 --> 00:05:53,474
See you later!

78
00:05:54,218 --> 00:05:55,412
Do your best!

79
00:05:55,786 --> 00:05:57,617
Study hard!

80
00:06:07,731 --> 00:06:09,096
<i>That's right...</i>

81
00:06:09,166 --> 00:06:12,192
<i>I come from the same Uchiha clan</i>
<i>as Elder Brother...</i>

82
00:06:21,345 --> 00:06:22,835
<i>I won't lose to Elder Brother!</i>

83
00:06:35,692 --> 00:06:37,455
<i>I'm pretty late...</i>

84
00:07:05,289 --> 00:07:06,381
<i>What was that?</i>

85
00:07:06,657 --> 00:07:08,522
<i>I had the feeling</i>
<i>there was someone there...</i>

86
00:07:13,030 --> 00:07:16,864
<i>The lights are out.</i>
<i>Even though it's not time for bed...</i>

87
00:07:22,372 --> 00:07:23,361
What's this?!

88
00:07:34,618 --> 00:07:36,677
W-What's this?!

89
00:07:43,193 --> 00:07:45,559
<i>What in the world is this?!</i>

90
00:07:57,608 --> 00:07:59,769
Uncle... Auntie...

91
00:08:04,214 --> 00:08:06,114
Father... Mother...!

92
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:19,151
Father? Mother?

93
00:08:21,565 --> 00:08:22,554
Aren't you here?

94
00:08:57,367 --> 00:08:58,527
<i>There's somebody here!</i>

95
00:09:07,411 --> 00:09:08,503
<i>Move!</i>

96
00:09:09,680 --> 00:09:10,669
<i>Move!</i>

97
00:09:12,149 --> 00:09:13,047
<i>Move!</i>

98
00:09:26,530 --> 00:09:27,963
Father! Mother!

99
00:09:54,524 --> 00:09:55,821
Elder Brother!

100
00:09:55,992 --> 00:09:58,552
Elder Brother!
Father and Mother are...!

101
00:09:59,096 --> 00:10:01,030
Why? For what reason?!

102
00:10:02,032 --> 00:10:03,761
Who in the world would do
something like this...?

103
00:10:09,539 --> 00:10:11,063
Elder Brother... What are you?

104
00:10:28,525 --> 00:10:30,891
What are you doing
Elder Brother!

105
00:10:31,628 --> 00:10:33,858
Foolish little brother...

106
00:10:42,405 --> 00:10:43,963
Mangekyo Sharingan!

107
00:11:01,691 --> 00:11:02,783
My legs...!

108
00:11:15,572 --> 00:11:17,039
Stop!

109
00:11:17,374 --> 00:11:18,841
Elder Brother!

110
00:11:18,908 --> 00:11:21,399
Don't make me see this!

111
00:11:23,713 --> 00:11:24,771
Why...?

112
00:11:25,515 --> 00:11:27,244
Why did you, Elder Brother...?!

113
00:11:27,617 --> 00:11:29,175
No!

114
00:11:29,819 --> 00:11:31,446
No...

115
00:11:37,394 --> 00:11:39,487
Auntie! Uncle!

116
00:11:44,701 --> 00:11:46,328
Father! Mother!

117
00:11:46,703 --> 00:11:48,534
Stop it! Elder Brother!

118
00:11:49,806 --> 00:11:51,637
Don't kill Father and Mother!

119
00:12:36,686 --> 00:12:37,948
W-Why...

120
00:12:39,589 --> 00:12:42,558
Why did you...? Elder Brother...?

121
00:12:46,830 --> 00:12:50,664
To measure my abilities...

122
00:12:51,668 --> 00:12:58,039
Measure your abilities...?
Just for that?

123
00:13:01,711 --> 00:13:03,702
Are you saying that...

124
00:13:04,447 --> 00:13:07,280
Just for that...
you killed them all?

125
00:13:10,019 --> 00:13:12,214
That is of great importance.

126
00:13:14,324 --> 00:13:16,155
What do you mean...?

127
00:13:20,263 --> 00:13:22,254
Don't talk rubbish!

128
00:13:53,396 --> 00:13:54,385
<i>I'm scared...</i>

129
00:13:55,398 --> 00:13:56,490
<i>I'm scared!</i>

130
00:14:11,214 --> 00:14:13,774
Don't kill me...!

131
00:14:30,400 --> 00:14:31,867
D-Don't kill me!

132
00:14:32,836 --> 00:14:36,135
You are not even worth killing...

133
00:14:37,874 --> 00:14:40,069
Foolish little brother...

134
00:14:41,444 --> 00:14:46,108
If you want to kill me, begrudge me!
Hate me!

135
00:14:47,016 --> 00:14:50,747
And keep on surviving in
that unsightly manner...

136
00:14:51,588 --> 00:14:55,820
Just continue fleeing and fleeing
and hang onto your life!

137
00:15:18,381 --> 00:15:19,780
Shall we go outside...?

138
00:15:21,918 --> 00:15:24,284
<i>These guys aren't just anybody...</i>

139
00:15:30,693 --> 00:15:34,151
Itachi, it'll be a pain in the neck
if this kid moves around and...

140
00:15:34,731 --> 00:15:37,894
Maybe I better chop off
a leg just in case...

141
00:15:39,736 --> 00:15:40,964
<i>W-What did he say?!</i>

142
00:15:47,944 --> 00:15:49,138
Now then...

143
00:16:01,925 --> 00:16:03,153
Long time no see...

144
00:16:08,398 --> 00:16:09,695
Sasuke.

145
00:16:10,333 --> 00:16:12,995
Uchiha Itachi!

146
00:16:14,337 --> 00:16:16,635
Uchiha... Itachi?

147
00:16:21,477 --> 00:16:24,571
<i>The same as Sasuke...</i>
<i>An Uchiha...</i>

148
00:16:28,851 --> 00:16:31,945
Huh... Sharingan...

149
00:16:32,021 --> 00:16:34,717
And moreover,
he resembles you a lot...

150
00:16:35,992 --> 00:16:37,960
Who the heck is he?

151
00:16:39,562 --> 00:16:42,929
He's my younger brother.

152
00:16:45,868 --> 00:16:50,066
But I heard that the entire Uchiha clan
had been murdered.

153
00:16:51,975 --> 00:16:53,340
By you.

154
00:16:55,545 --> 00:16:59,606
Itachi Uchiha... I will kill you!

155
00:17:04,020 --> 00:17:08,423
<i>I must kill one certain man</i>
<i>without fail!</i>

156
00:17:09,859 --> 00:17:11,451
<i>That man...</i>

157
00:17:14,464 --> 00:17:16,398
<i>My elder brother...</i>

158
00:17:16,766 --> 00:17:24,537
<i>I thought I couldn't die...</i>
<i>without killing him, but...</i>

159
00:17:27,510 --> 00:17:29,603
<i>That's the guy that Sasuke</i>
<i>was saying...</i>

160
00:17:29,679 --> 00:17:31,510
<i>The man he wanted to kill...</i>

161
00:17:48,598 --> 00:17:50,429
It's just as you said...

162
00:17:51,534 --> 00:17:54,901
I held a grudge against you
and hated you.

163
00:17:55,538 --> 00:17:58,632
For the singular purpose of
killing you, I...

164
00:18:02,378 --> 00:18:03,436
I...

165
00:18:05,014 --> 00:18:06,504
have lived my life!

166
00:18:07,417 --> 00:18:08,406
Sasuke...!

167
00:18:14,190 --> 00:18:15,248
Chidori...?

168
00:18:15,725 --> 00:18:18,023
I will kill you!

169
00:18:26,869 --> 00:18:28,131
Die!

170
00:18:53,830 --> 00:18:56,560
<i>W-What's going on?!</i>

171
00:18:56,933 --> 00:18:59,993
<i>I can't believe that Sasuke's Jutsu</i>
<i>was so easily thwarted...</i>

172
00:19:02,238 --> 00:19:03,603
<i>This doesn't look good!</i>

173
00:19:04,607 --> 00:19:06,234
<i>I've got to do something!</i>

174
00:19:10,980 --> 00:19:14,074
Chakra permeates the air...

175
00:19:15,184 --> 00:19:16,651
I see...

176
00:19:16,853 --> 00:19:19,287
So this is the Nine Tailed Fox Chakra!

177
00:19:19,355 --> 00:19:20,219
You jerk!

178
00:19:20,289 --> 00:19:21,221
You're in the way!

179
00:19:23,860 --> 00:19:25,157
Sasuke!

180
00:19:25,528 --> 00:19:27,052
Darn it!

181
00:19:27,263 --> 00:19:28,628
<i>Ninja Art. Summo...</i>

182
00:19:28,698 --> 00:19:29,722
You're too slow!

183
00:19:32,535 --> 00:19:35,629
<i>Huh...? I can't feel the Chakra...</i>

184
00:19:36,305 --> 00:19:39,399
Darn! Darn! Why is it?!

185
00:19:40,209 --> 00:19:42,507
My sword Shark Skin
has the ability to...

186
00:19:42,578 --> 00:19:46,241
cut through and eat Chakra!

187
00:19:50,820 --> 00:19:52,481
It's a pain in the butt

188
00:19:52,555 --> 00:19:54,750
if the kid moves around
and uses Jutsu like that...

189
00:19:55,024 --> 00:19:57,117
Before these legs...

190
00:19:57,193 --> 00:19:59,957
Should I chop off these arms?

191
00:20:04,500 --> 00:20:06,593
<i>Why doesn't it emerge?!</i>

192
00:20:06,969 --> 00:20:08,436
It's pointless...

193
00:20:25,621 --> 00:20:26,610
What?

194
00:20:35,665 --> 00:20:39,601
You guys just don't know me much,
do you?

195
00:20:40,603 --> 00:20:44,699
This man Jiraiya does not fall victim
to any woman's allurement,

196
00:20:44,774 --> 00:20:47,641
but rather his forte is
winning women's affection!

197
00:20:48,578 --> 00:20:52,742
I'm not made to blindly follow after
a woman's feminine charm!

198
00:20:53,583 --> 00:20:56,143
When you get to my level,

199
00:20:56,219 --> 00:21:01,782
women yelp with delight
at my sex appeal!

200
00:21:09,365 --> 00:21:13,301
<i>A cycle of hardship, right?</i>

201
00:21:14,304 --> 00:21:18,263
<i>Inside, we were crying, right?</i>

202
00:21:19,576 --> 00:21:27,540
<i>But the one thing we won't give up</i>
<i>is the dream we've chosen, right?</i>

203
00:21:28,518 --> 00:21:30,611
<i>It's a secondary role,</i>

204
00:21:33,389 --> 00:21:36,415
<i>a role in the shadows</i>

205
00:21:36,860 --> 00:21:41,797
<i>But in reaching for that dream,</i>

206
00:21:41,931 --> 00:21:47,392
<i>let us stay centered,</i>
<i>let us stay true</i>

207
00:21:47,670 --> 00:21:52,573
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we hung on without giving up</i>

208
00:21:52,642 --> 00:21:57,545
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we kept coming back up</i>

209
00:21:57,614 --> 00:22:06,784
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we believed and dreamed</i>

210
00:22:07,223 --> 00:22:12,126
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we've seen fools</i>

211
00:22:12,195 --> 00:22:18,031
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we've stood in the shadows of others</i>

212
00:22:19,669 --> 00:22:29,806
<i>Now, it's our turn...</i>
<i>Let us bask in our dreams</i>

213
00:22:37,353 --> 00:22:38,752
Watch out, Sasuke!

214
00:22:38,821 --> 00:22:40,789
Naruto, don't help him.

215
00:22:40,857 --> 00:22:42,791
But... Sasuke is!

216
00:22:42,859 --> 00:22:49,526
It is your duty to watch
through this battle, Naruto.

217
00:22:49,599 --> 00:22:50,725
What?!

218
00:22:50,800 --> 00:22:52,631
This is his fight...

219
00:22:52,702 --> 00:22:57,469
This represents everything that
he has been carrying up to now.

220
00:22:57,941 --> 00:23:01,877
Next time: "Hate Among the Uchihas:
The Last of the Clan!"
